sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Gateway<br/>(Route/HTTPRoute)
    participant API as OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Engine as V1 AsyncLLM Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant PyTorch as PyTorch CPU Backend<br/>(in-process C++)
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over API,PyTorch: Flow 1: OpenAI Chat Completion Request

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP, Optional TLS
    KServe->>API: Forward request<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
    API->>API: AuthenticationMiddleware<br/>Validate API Key (if configured)
    API->>Engine: generate() call<br/>(in-process Python)
    Engine->>PyTorch: Tensor computation<br/>(Python/C++ FFI)
    PyTorch-->>Engine: Generated tokens
    Engine-->>API: Token stream
    API-->>KServe: SSE stream (streaming)<br/>or JSON response
    KServe-->>Client: Response

    Note over Engine,S3: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup

    Engine->>HF: GET model weights & tokenizer<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HF-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>Engine: Load to local filesystem
    Engine->>PyTorch: Load model weights<br/>(in-process Python/C++)
    PyTorch-->>Engine: Model ready

    alt S3 Model Source
        Engine->>S3: GET model weights<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID)
        S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    end

    Note over Client,API: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request

    participant GRPCClient as gRPC Client
    participant GRPC as gRPC Server<br/>50051/TCP Insecure

    GRPCClient->>GRPC: gRPC Inference Request<br/>HTTP/2 50051/TCP<br/>No TLS, No Auth
    GRPC->>Engine: generate() call<br/>(in-process Python)
    Engine->>PyTorch: Tensor computation<br/>(Python/C++ FFI)
    PyTorch-->>Engine: Generated tokens
    Engine-->>GRPC: Token stream
    GRPC-->>GRPCClient: gRPC Response<br/>HTTP/2 50051/TCP
